  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>\"Hero Tower\" is a game without regular monsters where you directly challenge bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>We have meticulously designed 13 unique bosses, each with its own distinct fighting style.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>Enjoy seamless and responsive 2D controls: evade attacks with rolls and jumps, while finding opportunities to strike back at enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>Both attacking and rolling consume stamina, so it's crucial to manage your stamina wisely.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516540/extras/93b5c0afbffdb6c483ae2fbe8011e8a7.avif?t=1691479109\" width=616 height=352 /></span>",
